<B>Newsgroups:</B>     rec.puzzles,sci.math
<B>Subject:</B>        Re: Random Points on a SPHERE
<B>From:</B>           <A HREF="mailto:kubo@zariski.harvard.edu">kubo@zariski.harvard.edu</A> (Tal Kubo)
<B>Date:</B>           3 May 93 03:49:58 EDT
<B>Organization:</B>   Dept. of Math, Harvard Univ.
